text: Sebastián Gorčík (born September 5, 1995) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Karlovy Vary of the Czech Extraliga. Gorčík made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Karlovy Vary during the 2014–15 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:HC Karlovy Vary players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards Category:1995 births Category:Living people
